          </p>
          <a href="#" class="mx-auto xl:m-0 text-md 2xl:text-xl font-RokiestRegular tracking-widest bg-[#ff00003a] rounded-md border border-[#a0262698] p-2 flex items-center gap-2 hover:bg-[#ff00005a] transition-colors duration-300">
